title: Members of L.A. Councilwoman Martinez's staff summoned to appear before grand jury
text:
Members of L.A. Councilwoman Martinez... Members of L.A. Councilwoman Martinez's staff summoned to appear before grand jury 34 min ago Read more: Los Angeles Times 
Federal prosecutors have issued subpoenas to members of Los Angeles City Councilwoman Nury Martinez's staff, asking them to appear before the grand jury to discuss her recent reelection campaign, a political advisor said Thursday. Roy Behr, Martinez's political consultant, told The Times that an unspecified number of staffers have been summoned. Start the conversation, or Read more at Los Angeles Times.
